deviceInfo.label: VMCI device
deviceInfo.summary: Device on the virtual machine PCI bus that provides support for the virtual machine communication interface

property.label: Management Interface IP Address
property.description: IP address for the Management Interface. Leave blank if using DHCP. Example: 192.168.10.4

property.label: Management Interface Subnet Mask
property.description: Subnet mask for the Management Interface. Leave blank if using DHCP. Example : 24 or 255.255.255.0

property.label: Default Gateway
property.description: Optional default gateway for the Management Network. Leave blank if using DHCP.
